<lb n="0170b08" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0170b09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0170b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0170b11" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1073 [cf. No. 901(Fasc. 6)]</head>
<lb n="0170b12" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0170005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享和年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】天永五年寫東寺三密藏本，【乙】天永四年寫東寺三密藏本，【丙】平安時代寫仁和寺藏本</note>何耶揭唎婆像法</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0170b13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0170b14" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT20p0170b1401">復次取淨<note n="0170006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00512;＝縶【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0170006"><lem>&CB00512;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">縶</rdg></app>不得截割。請一畫師最功能。勿
<lb n="0170b15" ed="T"/>還其價。香湯洗浴著新淨衣<note n="0170007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">與＝乞【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0170007"><lem>與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">乞</rdg></app><note n="0170008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝授【丙】</note><app n="0170008"><lem>受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">授</rdg></app>八戒。日
<lb n="0170b16" ed="T"/>日如是。於清淨處作一水壇。縱廣四肘<note place="inline">水壇之法如餘
<lb n="0170b17" ed="T"/>部說</note>&CB00057;師護身結界畢已。於其壇中燒種種香。
<lb n="0170b18" ed="T"/>散種種華供養已訖。於此壇內畫作菩薩。<note n="0170009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">其＋（菩薩）【甲】【乙】，〔其〕－【丙】</note><app n="0170009"><lem>其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">其菩薩</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0170b19" ed="T"/>身長佛一磔<note place="inline">長短正當以人一肘</note>總有四面。中菩薩面極
<lb n="0170b20" ed="T"/>令端正。作慈悲顏顏色赤白頭髮純青。左邊
<lb n="0170b21" ed="T"/>一面作大瞋怒黑色之面。狗牙上出頭髮<note n="0170010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">微＝使&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0170010"><lem>微</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">使</rdg></app>
<lb n="0170b22" ed="T"/>&CB00594;如火焰色。右邊一面作大笑顏。赤白端正
<lb n="0170b23" ed="T"/>似菩薩面。頭髮純青三面頭上。各戴天冠及
<lb n="0170b24" ed="T"/>著耳璫。其天冠上有一化佛結跏趺坐。中面
<lb n="0170b25" ed="T"/>頂上作碧馬頭仍令合口。菩薩頸下著寶瓔
<lb n="0170b26" ed="T"/>珞。項背圓光數重色作。左手屈臂手當乳前
<lb n="0170b27" ed="T"/>把紅蓮花。其蓮花與菩薩頭齊正臨左膊。其
<lb n="0170b28" ed="T"/>華臺上作一化佛。著緋袈裟結跏趺坐。項背
<lb n="0170b29" ed="T"/>有光。右手仰掌五指申。臂肘平屈。其手掌
<pb n="0170c" id="T20.1073.0170c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0170c01" ed="T"/>擎真陀摩尼<note place="inline">唐云如意寶</note>其珠團圓如作白色。赤色
<lb n="0170c02" ed="T"/>光炎圍繞其珠。於其右手正當珠下雨種種
<lb n="0170c03" ed="T"/>寶。其左膊上。著弊耶<note place="inline">二合</note>迦羅者摩<note place="inline">二合唐云虎皮</note>
<lb n="0170c04" ed="T"/>如著祇支。當右腋下掩皮結帶。更用虎皮縵
<lb n="0170c05" ed="T"/>其跨上。以外臂釧天衣裙等。皆如餘處畫菩
<lb n="0170c06" ed="T"/>薩法。如令菩薩端身正立紅蓮華上。空懸寶
<lb n="0170c07" ed="T"/>傘蓋菩薩頭上。其上空中畫作種種天音樂
<lb n="0170c08" ed="T"/>具。兩邊空中須陀會天舞蹈供養。畫此像時
<lb n="0170c09" ed="T"/>用香汁畫。皮膠不當用。叉以蘇木佉子<note place="inline">唐云芸臺</note>擣
<lb n="0170c10" ed="T"/>以為末。極令微細用酪<note place="inline">作酪殘汁也</note>汁。和如和&CB00595;
<lb n="0170c11" ed="T"/>法。用何耶揭唎婆心&CB00057;。&CB00057;三七遍已。其病
<lb n="0170c12" ed="T"/>人空腹腹之。腹內所有一切毒虫悉皆吐出。
<lb n="0170c13" ed="T"/>又畫作像法。取新瓦雜瓶未曾用。瓶染作青
<lb n="0170c14" ed="T"/>色。其瓦瓶上畫作阿耶揭唎婆觀世音像。其
<lb n="0170c15" ed="T"/>像身高如來一磔<note place="inline">等人一肘</note>畫作四箇歡喜之面。左
<lb n="0170c16" ed="T"/>邊一面畫作黑色。眼<note n="0170011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">精＝睛&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0170011"><lem>精</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">睛</rdg></app>綠色狗牙上出。右
<lb n="0170c17" ed="T"/>邊一面畫作赤色。名喫&CB00057;面。當中前面作菩
<lb n="0170c18" ed="T"/>薩面。極令端正。畫作白色。離像頂上懸於空
<lb n="0170c19" ed="T"/>中。畫作青面。出口吐寶珠。其四頭上各戴寶
<lb n="0170c20" ed="T"/>冠。其寶冠上皆化佛坐。菩薩左手把於蓮華。
<lb n="0170c21" ed="T"/>屈肘向上捧在膊前。右臂垂下五指皆申。施
<lb n="0170c22" ed="T"/>無畏<note n="0170012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（印）＋手【甲】</note><app n="0170012"><lem>手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">印手</rdg></app>。兩手<note n="0170013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">腕＝捖【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0170013"><lem>腕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">捖</rdg></app>上皆作寶釧。其像項下著
<lb n="0170c23" ed="T"/>寶瓔珞。身分莊嚴如餘處說觀世音身莊嚴
<lb n="0170c24" ed="T"/>之法。其像立在寶蓮花上。作此像已。從白月
<lb n="0170c25" ed="T"/>十日起首食大麥乳糜。後十三日十四日十
<lb n="0170c26" ed="T"/>五日。三日<note n="0170014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔三〕－【丙】</note><app n="0170014"><lem>三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>夜斷食。取<note n="0170015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑＝婆【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0170015"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">婆</rdg></app>迦比遮香乾陀
<lb n="0170c27" ed="T"/>那句利華&CB00057;此二物。一&CB00057;一投當前面上至
<lb n="0170c28" ed="T"/>八千遍。其面口中放出<note n="0170016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0170016"><lem>大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>光明。<note n="0170017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（其光）＋圍【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0170017"><lem>圍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">其光圍</rdg></app>繞&CB00057;師
<lb n="0170c29" ed="T"/>身。已還入像口。於其口中出如意珠。即收取
<pb n="0171a" id="T20.1073.0171a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0171a01" ed="T"/><note n="0171001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之＝此【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171001"><lem>之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">此</rdg></app>珠已。即得十四千歲壽命。得七寶轉輪聖
<lb n="0171a02" ed="T"/>王。命終以後生安樂國。從觀世音足下而坐。
<lb n="0171a03" ed="T"/>又有一法當乞食喫喫大麥乳糜誦七萬遍。
<lb n="0171a04" ed="T"/>一萬遍時毘那耶迦即得被縛。第二萬遍&CB00057;
<lb n="0171a05" ed="T"/>法成就。第三萬遍即得安善那摩那熾羅藥
<lb n="0171a06" ed="T"/>法成就。三日三夜不食。作法手把其藥。正&CB00057;
<lb n="0171a07" ed="T"/>藥時。藥中若現三種相者。即知藥成。三相者
<lb n="0171a08" ed="T"/>謂煖煙焰。即得成就安陀羅<note n="0171002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔陀〕－【丙】</note><app n="0171002"><lem>陀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>那。昇空而去
<lb n="0171a09" ed="T"/>得成就持&CB00057;仙人。自在得入阿脩羅宮。第四
<lb n="0171a10" ed="T"/>萬遍離地四指而行自在。第五萬遍則得隨
<lb n="0171a11" ed="T"/>意昇空行。第六萬遍即得千歲活。&CB00057;師成就
<lb n="0171a12" ed="T"/>&CB00057;仙。<note n="0171003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔人〕－【丙】</note><app n="0171003"><lem>人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>隨其所作任運皆成。一切所呼喚者
<lb n="0171a13" ed="T"/>皆來。第七萬遍&CB00057;師即得頭髮變作螺髮成
<lb n="0171a14" ed="T"/>就。隨其所須應念即至。親近承事於觀世音。
<lb n="0171a15" ed="T"/>即知三世一切眾生死此生彼。即得成就。<note n="0171004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔若〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171004"><lem>若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0171a16" ed="T"/>又法若欲打西<note place="inline">去音</note>若<note place="inline">若耶反</note>者。何耶揭唎婆像
<lb n="0171a17" ed="T"/>前三日三夜斷食香摩壇上。種種香花。以淨
<lb n="0171a18" ed="T"/>飲食乳粥&CB00031;等種種供養。擣娑闍羅<note n="0171005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑＝婆【甲】，〔娑〕－【丙】</note><app n="0171005"><lem>娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">婆</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>香。以
<lb n="0171a19" ed="T"/>白蜜和為八千丸。&CB00057;一<note n="0171006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔丸〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171006"><lem>丸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>香一遍已。投火中
<lb n="0171a20" ed="T"/>燒。如是香盡。彼西<note n="0171007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惹＝若【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0171007"><lem>惹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">若</rdg></app>眾尋即初見變為馬
<lb n="0171a21" ed="T"/>頭。更經少時。轉為何耶揭哩婆頭。&CB00057;師奇上
<lb n="0171a22" ed="T"/>向彼眾時。一切西<app source="0171007" type="＊"><lem>惹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">若</rdg></app>眾悉皆散滅。又法先
<lb n="0171a23" ed="T"/>以大麥<note n="0171008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔與牛〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171008"><lem>與牛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>喫已。取<note n="0171009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔糞〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171009"><lem>糞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>中麥洗乾誠擣煮
<lb n="0171a24" ed="T"/>為乳糜。從白月一日食此乳糜。至十三日即
<lb n="0171a25" ed="T"/>斷不食。何耶揭哩婆像前。以塗香塗地散種
<lb n="0171a26" ed="T"/>種花。燒諸名香。種種飲食供養畢已。取迦
<lb n="0171a27" ed="T"/>比闍香擣為細末。水和為丸。數滿八千。取迦
<lb n="0171a28" ed="T"/>地羅木為柴燃火。取一香丸一&CB00057;一投。於火
<lb n="0171a29" ed="T"/>中燒。如是乃至八千丸。盡其炭變為蘇跋那
<pb n="0171b" id="T20.1073.0171b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0171b01" ed="T"/>金黃。重百千兩。又法若欲喫他&CB00057;者。取己身
<lb n="0171b02" ed="T"/>中小許血已。和白芥子為八千丸。黑月十四
<lb n="0171b03" ed="T"/>日。一日不食。取佉陀羅木鑪中燃火。取前白
<lb n="0171b04" ed="T"/>芥子丸。一&CB00057;一丸投火中燒。如是乃至芥子
<lb n="0171b05" ed="T"/>丸盡。一切諸&CB00057;悉皆喫盡<note place="inline">喫云外國語也。即同大唐破滅語訓。他者是外
<lb n="0171b06" ed="T"/>道也</note>又法但誦&CB00057;。行於曠野處及諸沙<note n="0171010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">磧＝碃【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171010"><lem>磧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">碃</rdg></app>。所須
<lb n="0171b07" ed="T"/>飲食自然而出。又法日月蝕時。取淨牛蘇一
<lb n="0171b08" ed="T"/>兩新瓦&CB00425;盛。即把此&CB00425;仰看日月。&CB00057;&CB00425;中蘇
<lb n="0171b09" ed="T"/>乃至蘇煖。或煙火出。當爾之時即飲此蘇服
<lb n="0171b10" ed="T"/>此蘇已。隨欲詣處舉意即至。若常誦此&CB00057;。一
<lb n="0171b11" ed="T"/>切怖畏得無所畏。所有障難悉皆解脫。又法
<lb n="0171b12" ed="T"/>若患路陀瘡<note place="inline">患此瘡者悉皆死也</note>及諸毒蛇之所&CB00599;者<note place="inline"><note n="0171011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此蛇＝蛇此【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171011"><lem>此蛇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">蛇此</rdg></app>
<lb n="0171b13" ed="T"/>人<note n="0171012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見即＝即人【丙】</note><app n="0171012"><lem>見即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">即人</rdg></app>死</note>或患健毘吒雞瘡。此等諸瘡&CB00057;黃土&CB00410;。
<lb n="0171b14" ed="T"/>滿一千遍。塗其瘡上即得除差。一切怖畏心
<lb n="0171b15" ed="T"/>念即得除。又法若人忽逢一切水難。心念即
<lb n="0171b16" ed="T"/>得不被沈溺。如是等法不可廣說。隨意即成。
<lb n="0171b17" ed="T"/>若造大曼荼羅者。不得行欲。</p>
<lb n="0171b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171b1801" type="dharani">賀耶揭哩婆療病印<note place="inline">二手內縛&CB00594;二中<note n="0171013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔指〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171013"><lem>指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>頭。相合並屈二大指。各以二頭指屈
<lb n="0171b19" ed="T"/>握二大指甲根。頭指甲<note n="0171014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔皆〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171014"><lem>皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>背相著</note></p>
<lb n="0171b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171b2001" type="dharani"><note n="0171015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（一）細註【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171015"><lem>唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>鶻嚕<note n="0171016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚧＋（二）細註【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171016"><lem>嚧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">嚧<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app>鳩盧馱<note place="inline">去音</note>那<note place="inline">三</note>嗚&CB00292;泮<note place="inline">四</note><note n="0171017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑&CB00085;賀＝莎去訶五【甲】【乙】，莎訶五【丙】</note><note n="0171017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑&CB00085;賀＝莎去訶五【甲】【乙】，＝莎訶五【丙】</note><app n="0171017"><lem>娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0171b21" ed="T"/>賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">莎去訶五</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">莎訶五</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0171b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171b2201" type="dharani"><note n="0171018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＝何【丙】</note><app n="0171018"><lem>賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">何</rdg></app>耶揭唎婆乞食印<note place="inline">仰左手各&CB00594;五指。將右手下向以中指無名<note n="0171019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">指＋（大指）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171019"><lem>指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">指大指</rdg></app>頭。
<lb n="0171b23" ed="T"/>各<note n="0171020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔各〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171020"><lem>各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>相拄<note n="0171021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔著〕－【丙】</note><app n="0171021"><lem>著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0171b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171b2401" type="dharani">唵是那耶<note place="inline">二句誦二七遍</note></p>
<lb n="0171b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171b2501"><note n="0171022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲乙丙三本已上乃至次十二字作夾註</note><note n="0171022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（已上二印可在解禁刀印之次）十二字本文＝（已上二印可在解禁刀印之次）十二字夾註【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171022"><lem>已上二印可在解禁刀印之次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><note place="inline">已上二印可在解禁刀印之次</note></rdg></app>。若作此法先
<lb n="0171b26" ed="T"/>當縛禁毘那夜迦。當對賀耶揭哩婆像前。取
<lb n="0171b27" ed="T"/><note n="0171023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">後＝蕤&M062403;【原】，俊【甲】，蕤【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0171023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後＝蕤&M062403;【原】，＝俊【甲】，＝蕤【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171023"><lem>後</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">蕤</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俊</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">蕤</rdg></app>木長八指截。燒火焰出。取安悉香作八百
<lb n="0171b28" ed="T"/>丸。一丸一&CB00057;一投火中。乃至香盡。毘那夜迦。
<lb n="0171b29" ed="T"/>即自被縛&CB00057;曰。</p>
<pb n="0171c" id="T20.1073.0171c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0171c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171c0101" type="dharani">歸命跢姪他<note place="inline">一</note>主<note n="0171024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚕＝魯【甲】＊</note><app n="0171024"><lem>嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">魯</rdg></app>主<app source="0171024" type="＊"><lem>嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">魯</rdg></app><note place="inline">二</note>毘主嚕<note n="0171025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（毘）＋主【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171025"><lem>主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">毘主</rdg></app>嚕<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0171c02" ed="T"/>伽跢耶莎<note place="inline"><note n="0171026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（上音）＋四【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171026"><lem>四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">上音四</rdg></app></note>摩訶婆<note place="inline">去音</note>羅<note place="inline">五</note>薩婆毘<note n="0171027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔知〕－【乙】</note><app n="0171027"><lem>知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0171028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">那＝耶【甲】，那＋（二合）細註【丙】</note><app n="0171028"><lem>那</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">耶</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">那<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>
<lb n="0171c03" ed="T"/>毘那夜乾<note place="inline">上音六</note>皤吒婆謨枯知<note place="inline">去音二合七</note>步跢<note place="inline">去音</note>
<lb n="0171c04" ed="T"/>耶泮<note place="inline">八</note></p>
<lb n="0171c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171c0501">若人夜失不淨。取於白線&CB00057;八百遍。後作&CB00057;
<lb n="0171c06" ed="T"/>索。一&CB00057;一結為三七結。即用繫腰。更不漏失。
<lb n="0171c07" ed="T"/>&CB00057;曰。</p>
<lb n="0171c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171c0801" type="dharani"><note n="0171029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">丙本歸命二字作細字</note><note n="0171029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（歸命）二字本文＝（歸命）二字細字【丙】</note><app n="0171029"><lem>歸命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><note place="inline">歸命</note></rdg></app>多姪他<note place="inline">一</note>勃地勃地<note place="inline">二</note>素勃地<note place="inline">三</note>因達&CB00074;
<lb n="0171c09" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>勃地<note place="inline">四</note>摩迷輸<note place="inline">上音</note>迦&CB00771;<note place="inline">上音二合五</note>婆羅謀者
<lb n="0171c10" ed="T"/>都<note place="inline">六</note>莎<note place="inline">去</note>訶</p>
<lb n="0171c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171c1101">又法&CB00057;袈裟誦一七遍。已結作一結。即得護
<lb n="0171c12" ed="T"/>身成就&CB00057;曰<note place="inline">歸命</note>。</p>
<lb n="0171c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0171c1301" type="dharani">哆姪他<note place="inline">一</note>訶<note place="inline">去音</note>哩訶<note place="inline">去音</note>哩<note place="inline">二</note>無訶<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00074;<note place="inline">三</note>句訶
<lb n="0171c14" ed="T"/><note place="inline">去</note>&CB00074;<note place="inline">四</note>薩婆突瑟擔<note place="inline">二合五</note>瞻<note n="0171030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆＝波【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0171030"><lem>婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">波</rdg></app>夜弭<note place="inline">上六</note>夜跋竭
<lb n="0171c15" ed="T"/><note n="0171031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01836;＝&CB14273;【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171031"><lem>&CB01836;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&CB14273;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>地<note place="inline">七</note>那文社弭<note place="inline">八</note>莎<note place="inline">去</note>訶<note place="inline">已上<note n="0171032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">了＝可【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0171032"><lem>了</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">可</rdg></app>寫隨誦成驗之次</note></p>
